  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"shape\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-shape\"></span>\n<h1>shape<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#shape\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">shape</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/tensor/attribute.py#L65\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Get the shape of the input.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-text notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span>Case1:\n    Given N-D Tensor:\n        input = [ [1, 2, 3, 4], [5, 6, 7, 8] ]\n\n    Then:\n        input.shape = [2, 4]\n\nCase2:\n    Given SelectedRows:\n        input.rows = [0, 4, 19]\n        input.height = 20\n        input.value = [ [1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6] ]  # inner tensor\n    Then:\n        input.shape = [3, 2]\n</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p><strong>input</strong> (<em>Tensor</em>) – The input can be N-D Tensor or SelectedRows with data type bool, bfloat16, float16, float32, float64, int32, int64. If input variable is type of SelectedRows, returns the shape of it’s inner tensor.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">\n           Returns\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\">\n<p>The shape of the input variable.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Return type\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p>Tensor</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-pycon notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">numpy</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">np</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">paddle</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">enable_static</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">inputs</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">static</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"x\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">dtype</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"float32\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">output</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">inputs</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">static</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Executor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">CPUPlace</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">exe</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">static</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">default_startup_program</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">img</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ones</span><span class=\"p\">((</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">))</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">astype</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">float32</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">res</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">exe</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">static</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">default_main_program</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> <span class=\"n\">feed</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"s1\">'x'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">img</span><span class=\"p\">},</span> <span class=\"n\">fetch_list</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">[array([  3, 100, 100], dtype=int64)]</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"section\">\n<h2>Used in the guide/tutorials<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usedintheguidetutorials\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">¶</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/documentation/docs/en/guides/jit/basic_usage_en.html\">基本用法</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>"
